  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA99-kiḷavi">itu paruvaṅkaṇ ṭāṟṟāḷāya talaiviyait tōḻi paruvamaṉṟeṉṟu vaṟpuṟuttiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante comforted HER, who was unable to bear it when seeing the season, by saying it was not the season.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA99">
<l>            nīraṟa vaṟanta nirampā nīḷiṭait</l>
<l>            tukilvirit taṉṉa veyilavi ruruppi</l>
<l>            ṉañcuvarap parikkum veñcura miṟantōr</l>
<l>            tāmvarat teḷitta paruvaṅ kāṇvara</l>
<l>            vituvō veṉṟiciṉ maṭantai matiyiṉṟu </l>
<l>            maṟantukaṭaṉ mukanta kamañcūṉ māmaḻai</l>
<l>            poṟuttal cellā tiṟutta vaṇpeyal</l>
<l>            kāreṉ ṟayarnta vuḷḷamoṭu tērvila</l>
<l>            piṭavuṅ koṉṟaiyuṅ kōṭalu</l>
<l>            maṭava vākaliṉ malarntaṉa palavē.</l>
    </lg>
       <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“[Is] this”,</l>
<l rend="indent4">you say, girl,</l>
<l rend="indent3">“since it comes to be seen,</l>
<l>the season of which he made clear he would come,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who traversed the hot desert, where one hastens,</l>
<l rend="indent3">for fear comes up,</l>
<l rend="indent2">through the shining heat of the sunlight [white-hot] like cloth</l>
<l rend="indent2">spread out [to dry] on the endless long way that has fallen dry</l>
<l rend="indent3">as the water subsided?”</l>
<l>– Because they [are] foolish, many of them have flowered:</l>
<l>the Piṭavu and the Laburnum and the white Malabar lily</l>
<l rend="indent">that have no discrimination, with [their] minds immersed in</l>
<l rend="indent3">[the thought]</l>
<l rend="indent2">“rainy season”, with liberal raining,</l>
<l rend="indent3">when the fully pregnant dark clouds</l>
<l rend="indent2">that have drawn [water] from the sea, thoughlessly(?)<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">matiyiṉṟu</term>: shall we take the n.sg. here as a mark of the adverb?</note></l>
<l rend="indent2">having forgotten [you?], tarry, [full to] the breaking point<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">poṟuttal cellātu</term>: "since bearing does not go" = "is impossible"?</note>.</l>
        </lg>
         </div>
